{
  "slug": "the-short-seeress-prophecy",
  "key": "TheShortSeeressProphecy",
  "title": {
    "on": "Völuspá in skamma",
    "ru": "Краткое Прорицание вёльвы",
    "en": "The Short Seeress' Prophecy"
  },
  "description": {
    "on": "",
    "ru": "В живых оставалось одиннадцать асов, когда Бальдр пал у смерти бугра; обещал тогда Вали за брата отмстить, и поразил он брата убийцу.",
    "en": "\"Eleven in number the gods were known, When Baldr o'er the hill of death was bowed; And this to avenge was Vali swift, When his brother's slayer soon he slew.\""
  },
  "source": {
    "on": "",
    "ru": "Древнеисландский текст, ред. Guðni Jónsson. Текст на русском языке в переводе А. И. Корсуна",
    "en": "An ancient Icelandic text, edited by Guðni Jónsson.\nTranslation by Henry Adams Bellows."
  },
  "texts": {
    "on": [
      {
        "id": "1",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "1.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Váru ellifu",
          "æsir talðir,",
          "Baldr er hné,",
          "við banaþúfu;",
          "þess lézk Váli",
          "verðr at hefna,",
          "síns of bróður",
          "sló hann handbana.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "2",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "2.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Var Baldrs faðir",
          "Burs arfþegi,",
          "Freyr átti Gerði,",
          "hon var Gymis dóttir,",
          "jötna ættar,",
          "ok Aurboðu;",
          "þó var Þjazi,",
          "þeira frændi,",
          "skrautgjarn jötunn,",
          "hans var Skaði dóttir.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "3",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "3.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Margt segjum þér",
          "ok munum fleira;",
          "vörumk, at viti svá.",
          "Viltu enn lengra?\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "4",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "4.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Haki var Hveðnu",
          "hóti beztr sona,",
          "en Hveðnu var",
          "Hjörvarðr faðir;",
          "Heiðr ok Hrossþjófr",
          "Hrímnis kindar.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "5",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "5.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Eru völur allar",
          "frá Viðolfi,",
          "vitkar allir",
          "frá Vilmeiði,",
          "seiðberendr",
          "frá Svarthöfða,",
          "jötnar allir",
          "frá Ymi komnir.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "6",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "6.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Margt segjum þér",
          "ok munum fleira;",
          "vörumk, at viti svá.",
          "Viltu enn lengra?\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "7",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "7.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Varð einn borin",
          "í árdaga",
          "rammaukinn mjök",
          "rögna kindar;",
          "níu báru þann",
          "naddgöfgan mann",
          "jötna meyjar",
          "við jarðar þröm.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "8",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "8.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Hann Gjalp of bar,",
          "hann Greip of bar,",
          "bar hann Eistla",
          "ok Eyrgjafa,",
          "hann bar Ulfrún",
          "ok Angeyja,",
          "Imdr ok Atla",
          "ok Járnsaxa.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "9",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "9.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Sá var aukinn",
          "jarðar megni,",
          "svalköldum sæ",
          "ok sónardreyra.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "10",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "10.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Margt segjum þér",
          "ok munum fleira;",
          "vörumk, at viti svá.",
          "Viltu enn lengra?\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "11",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "11.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Ól ulf Loki",
          "við Angrboðu,",
          "en Sleipni gat",
          "við Svaðilfara;",
          "eitt þótti skass",
          "allra feiknast,",
          "þat var bróður frá",
          "Býleists komit.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "12",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "12.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Loki át hjarta",
          "lindi brenndu,",
          "fann hann halfsviðinn",
          "hugstein konu;",
          "varð Loftr kviðugr",
          "af konu illri;",
          "þaðan er á foldu",
          "flagð hvert komit.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "13",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "13.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Haf gengr hríðum",
          "við himin sjalfan,",
          "líðr lönd yfir,",
          "en loft bilar;",
          "þaðan koma snjóvar",
          "ok snarir vindar;",
          "þá er í ráði,",
          "at rögn of þrjóti.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "14",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "14.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Varð einn borinn",
          "öllum meiri,",
          "sá var aukinn",
          "jarðar megni;",
          "þann kveða stilli",
          "stórúðgastan",
          "sif sifjaðan",
          "sjötum görvöllum.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "15",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "15.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Þá kemr annarr",
          "enn máttkari,",
          "þó þori ek eigi",
          "þann at nefna;",
          "fáir séa nú",
          "fram of lengra",
          "en Óðinn mun",
          "ulfi mæta.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      }
    ],
    "ru": [
      {
        "id": "1",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "1.",
        "lines": [
          "\"В живых оставалось",
          "одиннадцать асов,",
          "когда Бальдр пал",
          "у смерти бугра;",
          "обещал тогда Вали",
          "за брата отмстить,",
          "и поразил он",
          "брата убийцу.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "2",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "2.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Бальдра отец",
          "был наследником Бура,",
          "Фрейр в жены взял Герд,",
          "Гюмира дочь,",
          "етуна родом,",
          "жена его Аурбода;",
          "Тьяци их родич,",
          "к сокровищам жадный,",
          "дочерью Тьяци",
          "Скади была.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "3",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "3.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Я много сказала,",
          "но больше скажу, —",
          "ты знать это должен;",
          "будешь ли слушать?\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "4",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "4.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Хаки был сыном",
          "достойнейшим Хведны,",
          "а Хведны отец",
          "Хьервардом звался,",
          "Хейд и Хросстьов —",
          "потомки Хримнира.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "5",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "5.",
        "lines": [
          "\"От Видольва род свой",
          "все вельвы ведут,",
          "от Вильмейда род",
          "ведут все провидцы,",
          "а все чародеи —",
          "от Черной Главы,",
          "а етунов племя —",
          "от Имира корня.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "6",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "6.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Я много сказала,",
          "но больше скажу, —",
          "ты знать это должен:",
          "будешь ли слушать?\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "7",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "7.",
        "lines": [
          "\"В давние годы",
          "родился однажды",
          "могучий герой",
          "из рода богов;",
          "дочери етунов —",
          "девять их было —",
          "родили его",
          "у края земли.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "8",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "8.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Родила его Гьяльп,",
          "родила его Грейн,",
          "родила его Эйстла,",
          "родила его Эйргьява,",
          "родила его Ангейя,",
          "Атла и Ульврун,",
          "Имд и Ярнсакса",
          "героя родили.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "9",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "9.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Взял силу земли он,",
          "студеного моря",
          "и силу кабаньей",
          "жертвенной крови.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "10",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "10.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Я много сказала,",
          "но больше скажу, —",
          "ты знать это должен;",
          "будешь ли слушать?\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "11",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "11.",
        "lines": [
          "\"От Ангрбоды Локи",
          "Волка родил,",
          "а Слейпнир — сын Локи",
          "от Свадильфари;",
          "еще одно чудище,",
          "самое злое,",
          "на свет рождено",
          "Бюлейста братом.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "12",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "12.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Найдя на костре",
          "полусгоревшее",
          "женщины сердце,",
          "съел его Локи;",
          "так Лофт зачал",
          "от женщины злой;",
          "отсюда пошли",
          "все ведьмы на свете.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "13",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "13.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Ветер вздымает",
          "до неба валы,",
          "на сушу бросает их,",
          "небо темнеет;",
          "мчится буран,",
          "и бесятся вихри;",
          "это предвестья",
          "кончины богов.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "14",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "14.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Родился один",
          "самый могучий,",
          "силы земли",
          "питали его;",
          "самый, как слышно,",
          "великий властитель,",
          "родич для всех",
          "людей на земле.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "15",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "15.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Но будет еще",
          "сильнейший из всех,",
          "имя его",
          "назвать я не смею;",
          "мало кто ведает,",
          "что совершится",
          "следом за битвой",
          "Одина с Волком.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      }
    ],
    "en": [
      {
        "id": "1",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "1.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Eleven in number",
          "the gods were known,",
          "When Baldr o'er the hill",
          "of death was bowed;",
          "And this to avenge",
          "was Vali swift,",
          "When his brother's slayer",
          "soon he slew.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "2",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "2.",
        "lines": [
          "\"The father of Baldr",
          "was the heir of Bur,",
          "Freyr's wife was Gerth,",
          "the daughter of Gymir,",
          "Of the giants' brood,",
          "and Aurbotha bore her;",
          "To these as well",
          "was Thjazi kin,",
          "The dark-loving giant;",
          "his daughter was Skathi.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "3",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "3.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Much have I told thee,",
          "and further will tell;",
          "There is much that I know;",
          "wilt thou hear yet more?\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "4",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "4.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Heith and Hrossthjof,",
          "the children of Hrimnir.",
          "Of Hvethna's sons",
          "Haki was best by a bit,",
          "by Hjorvarth was",
          "Hvethna's father.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "5",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "5.",
        "lines": [
          "\"The sybils arose",
          "from Vitholf's race,",
          "From Vilmeith all",
          "the seers are,",
          "And the workers of charms",
          "are Svarthofthi's children,",
          "And from Ymir sprang",
          "the giants all.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "6",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "6.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Much have I told thee,",
          "and further will tell;",
          "There is much that I know;",
          "wilt thou hear yet more?\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "7",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "7.",
        "lines": [
          "\"One there was born",
          "in the bygone days,",
          "Of the race of the gods,",
          "and great was his might;",
          "Nine giant women,",
          "at the world's edge,",
          "Once bore the man",
          "so mighty in arms.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "8",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "8.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Gjolp there bore him,",
          "Greip there bore him,",
          "Eistla bore him,",
          "and Eyrgjafa,",
          "Ulfrun bore him,",
          "and Angeyja,",
          "Imth and Atla,",
          "and Jarnsaxa.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "9",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "9.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Strong was he made",
          "with the strength of earth,",
          "With the ice-cold sea,",
          "and the blood of swine.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "10",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "10.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Much have I told thee,",
          "and further will tell;",
          "There is much that I know;",
          "wilt thou hear yet more?\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "11",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "11.",
        "lines": [
          "\"The wolf did Loki",
          "with Angrbotha win,",
          "And Sleipnir bore he",
          "to Svathilfari;",
          "The worst of marvels",
          "seemed the one",
          "That sprang from the brother",
          "of Byleist then.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "12",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "12.",
        "lines": [
          "\"A heart ate Loki,",
          "in the embers it lay,",
          "And half-cooked found he",
          "the woman's heart;",
          "With child from the woman",
          "Lopt soon was,",
          "And thence among men",
          "came the monsters all.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "13",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "13.",
        "lines": [
          "\"The sea, storm-driven,",
          "seeks heaven itself,",
          "O'er the earth it flows,",
          "the air grows sterile;",
          "Then follow the snows",
          "and the furious winds,",
          "For the gods are doomed,",
          "and the end is death.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "14",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "14.",
        "lines": [
          "\"One there was born,",
          "the best of all,",
          "And strong was he made",
          "with the strength of earth;",
          "The proudest is called",
          "the kinsman of men",
          "Of the rulers all",
          "throughout the world.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "15",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "15.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Then comes another,",
          "a greater than all,",
          "Though never I dare",
          "his name to speak;",
          "Few are they now",
          "that farther can see",
          "Than the moment when Othin",
          "shall meet the wolf.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      }
    ]
  }
}
